{
  "stem": "24268.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I and my sister went, even though we've been working for, they made the shop, they called [INAUDIBLE], which we work for.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were doing this, uniforms, shirts, whatever they need, underwear for the Wehrmacht, for the soldiers, for the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she was working one place and I was working.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But during the night, we've been able to stay together that night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And meantime, they told my mom there's gonna be a raid again for young girls, but I shouldn't-- we shouldn't be afraid.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our names are not on the list.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Meantime, I was with my sister and went home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, the whole shop was surrounded with SS.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they-- and they hided me, because I had a good voice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody loved to listen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One of the mechanics, which-- what they fixed the machines if something went wrong.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they hided me and two other-- three girls, a sister, I think, and some other, two friends.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Four girls were been hidden in this area, in this room, whatever the mechanics had.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where they work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where they were there before if they needed to be, they helped, and if somebody need to take care of the machines.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, I-- they hided me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden, somebody must have said something, or was it accidentally.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All of a sudden, I see black boots approaching me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said, come, come.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I knew I-- I was in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so that time when they got me surrounded, but they put me and the three girls in separate rooms, because they said that we're gonna be out.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so meantime, we waited and waited.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the-- my cousins' mom find out about this so quickly.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
